high_descs: Walk forward to face the round table.
Pick up the knife that is on the table, beside the fork.
Turn around, then face the stove top to your right.
Place the knife on the pan on the left side front burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan and knife from the stove.
Turn to the right, cross the room, face the coffee maker.
Place the pan and knife in the corner of the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the knife with the pan, place them in the corner of the counter top beside the coffee maker.

high_descs: Move forward to the black table.
Pick up the knife from the center of the table.
Carry the knife and turn around, then to the left to find the stove.
Place the knife in the pan in the front of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife from the stove.
Carry the pan and turn right, then face left to the coffee maker.
Place the pan and knife in the corner of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife in a pan and move them to the counter.

high_descs: Move to the table ahead of you
Pick up knife from the table
Move to the stove to the right of you
Place knife on a plate on the stove
Pick up plate with knife from the stove
Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Put plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on the counter.
